snippet.title: Snook Trailer
snippet.description:
Snook is an online, multiplayer, Snake-like IO game… [gulp…I mean… comparing it to the old Nokia Snake is like comparing Bruce Banner to the Hulk.]
It is a kill-or-be-killed, adrenaline-charged, multiplayer game that is pioneering NFT game characters. That means players’ performance directly affects the NFT face value (more about that below).

* Snook is available on desktop only. Mobile app will be available as soon as we get to it.


Play Snook: https://www.snook.gg/
Join our discord: https://discord.gg/snook
